.TH LOA-READING-SMART-GENERATE 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
reading smart generate \- Replace reading list using smart recommendations
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> reading smart generate
.br
alexandria> reading smart generate 8
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Builds a recommendation set from your interests and replaces the current reading list.
.TP
Optional count controls how many recommendations are used (default: 10).
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> reading smart generate
.TP
alexandria> reading smart generate 12
